  "title": "HR Consultant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Utilize various sourcing techniques and platforms to identify and attract candidates.</li><li>Conduct initial assessments, and screening candidates to determine their suitability for specific positions.</li><li>Ability to grasp commercial and business concepts quickly</li><li>Ability to understand the requirements of each available job opening and work with the team to source for the right talents within a designated point of  time </li><li>Develop effective sourcing strategies to successfully shortlist candidates for specific roles. Proactively build pipelines of candidate prospects for niche skillsets</li><li>Able to work in a lean team and be very resourceful and agile. </li><li>Be the ambassador of company's culture, provide a positive candidate experience throughout the recruitment process.</li><li>Other ad-hoc tasks assigned</li></ul><p><br />We are looking for individuals who are able to commit a minimum of 3 months and above. <br /><br />Interested applicants, please reach out: christine@caineseymour.com </p>",
